7985266262261.title: Saysh One - Winter Warm
7985266262261.description:
The Saysh One’s lightweight construction pairs woven jacquard textiles and microsuede touches for a breathable, everyday sneaker. The design is sculpted to fit the shape and form of the female foot, with a single heel piece and a snug lacing system, producing an elegant, graceful silhouette that’s both supporting and comforting.

The Saysh One is a snug fit. We recommend sizing up half a size.
